The persona and place files in this folder are original works by Kai Schlueter,
derived from but not reproducing the historical record of:

  Flaminio Scala - Il Teatro delle Favole Rappresentative (1611)
  Pier Maria Cecchini - Frutti delle moderne comedie (1628)
  Luigi Riccoboni - Histoire du Theatre Italien (1728)
  Carlo Goldoni - Memorie (1787)
